Excellent app. Sadly when I upgraded to the paid version I stopped getting notifications. This feature is very important to me. I'm happy to report that Mario, the developer, has been very responsive. I'm confident that he will make it work properly! I'll update this review when we get it fixed.
Exceptional, no better word to describe. The depth of tracking, including a diary, moods, and the improvement of health is amazing. I never leave reviews but this deserved one.

I found all of the features in this app to be extremely useful. I like seeing how much lifetime I've regained and money I've saved. I know how I feel, but having some straightforward stats that represent the tangibles of sobriety help to see the progress. I used the free version of this app for over 2 years. I just recently purchased the ad-free version of the app after realizing how long and how often I use it. The ads were so unobtrusive in the free version that I didnt even notice them.
This has been very helpful in my recovery...just got my badge for 10,000 hours! One moment at a time...

Brilliant app.. Love the health tracker. Recommend to anyone. I dint usually leave reviews this one deserves one.. Thanx whoever created this appüòÅüëç

Been off booze for four days after a very stressful time in my life. You need to be personally motivated as this is just a tool for focus and reflection.
THANK YOU

This app really is helping me more than group sessions ever did. I find the money saved function from not drinking to be especially motivating. I'm 33 and have been drinking dangerous levels of spirits daily since my early 20s but it's time to go clean. Recommended.

DL'ed this cuz of the amazing reviews - and I'm so glad! I'm getting so much more use out of it than I thought. There are SO many ways it keeps you motivated, so you never forget what you're working towards. It helps you see how much $ you're saving, how much health you're gaining day by day, and a place to enter your triggers or personal motivators. Plus like 20 other functions lol I just cannot say enough good things about this app! I paid for Pro cuz I want to support what u guys are doing ‚úä

Easy to use and keeps you informed of your benefits each step of the way. Get it....Buy the full version. You wont regret it. UPDATE !!! Almost seven months dry and the positive review hilds strong. Well pleased. Onwards and upwards. (Update....coming up for 10 months dry and still using this app. Nice one) Amendment.......460 + days sober now.

The app helps keep track of your progress to keep you on track with your goals. The journal entries and the game help immensely when times are getting tough. And the health monitor encourages you to keep with it as the visuals show your body recovering while giving helpful, positive information about every aspect that matters. Thanks to the developers. I'm getting my life back! Future integration with smart watches or other devices would be a powerful add-on.
